    <p class="text-sm">
      This system illustrates a common security pattern: messages protected in transit but vulnerable at processing points. 
      True end to end encryption would encrypt the message on your device in a way that only the recipient could decrypt it, 
      preventing intermediaries from reading content.
    </p>
